Hi, it’s Victoria! I am ecstatic to share; East will be taking limited realism clients a month! 

East is the pioneer of fine line delicate tattoos that has become popular in the last decade; but he actually started his career doing color & black and grey realism (and has won first place in world renowned tattoo conventions). 

He stopped doing realism to focus on his laser crisp line work; and since I started working with him I had been pleading him to do these realism portraits again. I hated that he was not sharing his incredible talent with the world. It took a whole year of convincing; but he finally agreed! 

If you’re interested in one of these from East, please book using the booking link and please email: east01tattoo@gmail.com with your story and several photo options.
